  <name>ld-decode</name>
  <summary>Software defined LaserDisc decoder</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ld-decode is a software defined LaserDisc decoder for RF captures of LaserDisc and other
      analog video formats. It processes raw RF samples to produce decoded video and audio.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>PAL and NTSC LaserDisc decoding</li>
      <li>Support for multiple analog video formats</li>
      <li>Advanced filtering and signal processing</li>
      <li>Video preservation and archival capabilities</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
